hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I'm in my first year at university price of drugs in america Ken is a graduate of the University of Missouri where he studied broadcast journalism. He loves the Bucs so much that he struggles to get a good night sleep when they lose. Ken's also an avid White Sox, Chicago Bulls, and U.S. Soccer fan. He's never lived in the Tampa area but has been to every game played in a neighboring state to his home for the past 8 years. On one instance before a preseason game in Kansas City, Ken had a 10 minute conversation with Bucs GM Mark Dominik. The Bucs went on to go 4-12. His advice to the GM was obviously well received.
